Package com.uddernetworks.emojide.gui.render

Class RenderEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uddernetworks.emojide.gui.render.RenderEngine
  • public class RenderEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    Has an internal loop to process RenderActions, to make the creation and editing of emoji messages much more efficient and consistent.

    • Method Detail

      • start

        public static void start()
        Starts the internal render loop of 1 RenderAction per second, processing RenderBreakpoints as soon as possible when they come up. If multiple RenderActions come up with the same editing status, message IDs, etc. the most recent one is processed to allow for much faster rendering, skipping useless 'frames' essential due to Discord's heavy rate limiting.

      • breakpoint

        public static void breakpoint​(java.lang.Runnable runnable)
        Queues a Runnable to invoke when the queue reaches it. This can be used for things like unblocking a method when a group of messages has been edited, among many other things, as the time taken to complete a group of actions may not be proportional to the amount of actions.
        Parameters:
        runnable - The Runnable to invoke
